== Welcome to iBoard4

iBoard 4 is the new generation iBoard version. Based on the latest RAILS and GEM features.
The project starts at Oct 2009 and will be developed (with slow pace) while continuing iBoard3-campus development.

There is no due date for iBoard 4 but the need to be as clean and streight forward as possible.

== Installing

# Please fetch and pull from Github (http://github.com/iboard/ib4)
# rake db:migrate
# rake db:seed
# Copy environments/development.rb.sample to environments/development.rb and edit to fit your needs
# script/server and login as root with password 'secret' and change root's profile
# start using ib4

== RDoc

You will find RDocs starting from doc/app/index.html

